## 6. Environment

- **OS:** Windows 11 / Linux / macOS
- **Runtime:** Python 3.11
- **Shell:** PowerShell (Windows) or Bash (Linux/macOS)
- **Containers:** Docker Desktop or Docker Engine
- **IDE:** Cursor / VS Code

